net.jini.export

Interface DynamicProxyCodebaseAccessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CodebaseAccessor, Remote

    public interface DynamicProxyCodebaseAccessor
extends CodebaseAccessor
    A marker interface for a dynamic proxy. Services that don't use a smart proxy, and utilize only a dynamic proxy, but still need a codebase to resolve interface classes should implement this interface.
    Author:
    peter
